init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and a side of bacon, you're wondering what happened to all the mugs.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and a dollop of whipped cream and think about it.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you find it, you're somewhere in the bottom third.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You shrug it off as a fluke and go back to your meal.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But then you notice that your name is no longer on the mug.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: In its place is the name of a different man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look at the other mugs and find that your name is removed from all of them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: At that moment, a cold chill runs up your spine.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You get up from the table and try to call your wife, but she doesn't answer.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He's definitely not a friend of yours.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You run through your memory to see if you've forgotten someone.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You go to your daughter Harper's room and find it empty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When you call out for her, a man answers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He is Harper's new stepfather and you've never met him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You think back to all the times she said, "Our daughter is the only thing we have in common.
